Battle Breakers

Endpoint: POST /api/v1/judge/battle-breakers

Body (raw, JSON):

    1 {
    2   "questionId": "60d5f1b3e7b3c1b6a8f0b1e2",
    3   "responses": [
    4     {
    5       "userId": "60d5f1b3e7b3c1b6a8f0b1e3",
    6       "attempt": "This is the user's attempt.",
    7       "status": "Correct"
    8     }
    9   ]

10 }

