Circuit Smashers

Endpoint: POST /api/v1/judge/circuit-smashers

Body (raw, JSON):

    1 {
    2   "schoolId": "60d5f1b3e7b3c1b6a8f0b1e4",
    3   "judgeId": "60d5f1b3e7b3c1b6a8f0b1e5",
    4   "marks": [
    5     {
    6       "criteriaId": "60d5f1b3e7b3c1b6a8f0b1e6",
    7       "mark": 10
    8     }
    9   ],

10 "totalMarks": 10
11 }

